1. transition => used to move smooth.

    transition-duration
    transition-timing-function
    transition-property
    transition-delay
    transition (short hand)

2. transform = used  how to show element dimensions

    transform
    transform-origin
    transform-style
    transform-box

    functions :

    (1) rotate => rotate(),rotateX(), rotateY(), rotateZ(), rotate3d()
    (2) skew => skew(), skewX(), skewY()
    (3) scale => scale(), scaleX(), scaleY(), scaleZ(), scale3d()
    (4) translate => translate(), translateX(), translateY(), translateZ(), translate3d()
    (5) matrix => matrix()
    (6) matrix3d => matrix3d()
    (7) perspective => perspective()

